年以下有期徒刑、拘役或9千元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/111%2c%e8%8b%97%e7%b0%a1%2c913%2c20220906%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,111,苗簡,913,20220906,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"苗簡","JNO":"913","JDATE":"20220906","JTITLE":"偽造文書"}